::Spears::

"AAHh haha  hahaha."  She was laughing and kept tickling him.  She 
tried to flip, but Striker had her pinned really well. She smiled and 
chuckled. She looked into his eyes and saw something, other than 
soot. But a fire that burned true.  Fire that would lead the way in 
the darkest of night and prove time and time again that the fire 
would never burn out.  

She felt her spark race for a moment.  She felt the overwhelming urge 
to kiss him.  She was afraid it would scare him off or he would tell 
her later that he wan't interested in her.  But she wanted to follow 
her spark.

She laughed and leaned forward.  She kisses him.  And she put her 
spark into that kiss.
